Returns the angle of the segment.



```js
segAng(segment_name: string, sketch_group: SketchGroup) -> number
```

### Examples

```js
const part001 = startSketchOn('XY')
  |> startProfileAt([4.83, 12.56], %)
  |> line([15.1, 2.48], %)
  |> line([3.15, -9.85], %, 'seg01')
  |> line([-15.17, -4.1], %)
  |> angledLine([segAng('seg01', %), 12.35], %)
  |> line([-13.02, 10.03], %)
  |> close(%)
  |> extrude(4, %)
```
